From d4b257a0517ddb39806e51afdeebff14d43f9381 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nate Myren <ntmyren@google.com>
Date: Mon, 3 Nov 2025 10:42:20 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] V2 Merge all permissions in a shared UID for every
 package in that UID

Since every package can use the permissions in the shared UID, even if
the given package didn't request it, every package should be treated in
UI as if they all have the total set of requested permissions

Test: atest PermissionTest23
Bug: 435737668
Flag: EXEMPT CVE_FIX
Relnote: cve fix
BUG: 456903810
Low Coverage Reason: unclear why coverage is not voted +2
